<li><a href="http://gslc.genetics.utah.edu/units/cloning/clickandclone/" class="external text" title="http://gslc.genetics.utah.edu/units/cloning/clickandclone/" rel="nofollow">Click and Clone</a>. Try it yourself in the virtual mouse cloning laboratory, from the <a href="/wiki/University_of_Utah" title="University of Utah">University of Utah</a>'s Genetic Science Learning Center</li>
<li><a href="http://edition.cnn.com/interactive/health/0108/cloning.timeline/content.html" class="external text" title="http://edition.cnn.com/interactive/health/0108/cloning.timeline/content.html" rel="nofollow">Cloning timeline</a>: from <a href="/wiki/CNN" title="CNN">CNN</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.nationalreview.com/document/document071602.asp" class="external text" title="http://www.nationalreview.com/document/document071602.asp" rel="nofollow">"Cloning Addendum: A statement on the cloning report issues by the President's Council on Bioethics,"</a> The National Review, <span class="mw-formatted-date" title="2002-07-15"><span class="mw-formatted-date" title="07-15"><a href="/wiki/July_15" title="July 15">July 15</a></span>, <a href="/wiki/2002" title="2002">2002</a></span> 8:45am</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/The_President%27s_Council_on_Bioethics" title="The President's Council on Bioethics">The President's Council on Bioethics</a></li>
